T* (This guide explains how to verify and turn on the Mackey Hall sound system.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (If the system is already on, no changes are needed.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Check Rack Power) Tj
T* (1. Go to the sound system rack.) Tj
T* (2. Find the red Power switch on the rack.) Tj
T* (3. If the switch is not lit red, turn it on.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Image: Rack Power Switch) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Check Amplifier Power) Tj
T* (1. Locate the amplifier in the rack \(third unit from the bottom\).) Tj
T* (2. Press the amplifier power button at the bottom-right.) Tj
T* (3. Confirm the button lights blue, which means the amplifier is on.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Image: Amplifier Power Button) Tj
T* () Tj
